high_descs: Turn completely around, walk to the small table at the end of the bed.
Pick up the small yellow pencil on the right.
Turn completely around, walk to the end of the bed, turn left, walk to the counter on the other side.
Put the pencil on the counter left of the clock on the front of the counter.
anns.task_desc: Move a pencil from the table to the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and walk forward to the small round table by the bed
Pick up the right most yellow pencil from the table
Turn around and walk forward then turn left and walk over to the large white shelf
Put the pencil on top of the white shelf
anns.task_desc: Put the pencil on the white shelf

high_descs: Turn and go to the left side of the bed the side with the lap top on it. Go to the small table next to the bed with the lamp on it.
Pick up the pencil that is to the right of the lamp but the one that is the farthest from the lamp
With the pencil in hand go to the shelf with the two clocks on it.
Place the pencil on the shelf to the left of the clock that is in front.
